{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-dgh-src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/cai-dat-thu-vien-ms-sql-jdbc-bang-maven","result":{"data":{"post":{"headings":[{"depth":2},{"depth":2},{"depth":3},{"depth":3},{"depth":3},{"depth":2}],"frontmatter":{"title":"Cài đặt thư viện MS SQL JDBC bằng Maven","path":"/cai-dat-thu-vien-ms-sql-jdbc-bang-maven","tags":["Java"],"excerpt":"Maven là 1 công cụ dùng để quản lý các thư viện, dự án, dependencies cho lập trình viên java, tương tự nuget của .NET và NPM của Nodejs.","created":"2021-10-19T00:00:00.000Z","createdPretty":"19 October, 2021","updated":"2021-10-19T00:00:00.000Z","updatedPretty":"19 October, 2021","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"sizes":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.9230769230769231,"src":"/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/7096b/project_tool_window_maven.png","srcSet":"/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/dc47e/project_tool_window_maven.png 200w,\n/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/9f2d5/project_tool_window_maven.png 400w,\n/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/7096b/project_tool_window_maven.png 653w","sizes":"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px"}}}},"html":"<h2>Dẫn nhập về Maven</h2>\n<p>Maven là 1 công cụ dùng để quản lý các thư viện, dự án, dependencies cho lập trình viên java, tương tự nuget của .NET và NPM của Nodejs.</p>\n<p>Tưởng tượng mỗi khi bạn thêm thư viện trong dự án Java, bạn phải lên mạng, tải file Jar thư viện đó về, import vào dự án...\nMột khi bạn muốn đổi version của thư viện đó, bạn phải lặp lại hành động này, quá là tốn thời gian và công sức. Maven thần thánh sẽ giúp bạn xử lý được vấn đề này thông qua vài bước config đơn giản.</p>\n<p>Hôm nay mình sẽ hướng dẫn cách dùng maven cơ bản để cài thư viện Microsoft JDBC Driver cho việc tương tác với database SQL Server.</p>\n<h2>Cách sử dụng maven trong IntelliJ</h2>\n<p>Mình không thích Eclipse cho lắm, nhưng về cơ bản, các bước thêm thư viện trong Eclipse vẫn sẽ giống Intellij. Phạm vi trong bài này mình sẽ chỉ hướng dẫn bằng IntelliJ thôi.\nMặc dù Intellij Ultimate có phí, nếu bạn là sinh viên, giáo viên và có mail <em>.edu.vn</em> thì có thể đăng ký dùng bản này miễn phí ở đây <a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/shop/eform/students\">(Đăng ký intellij Ultimate free)</a>, hoặc thậm chí bạn xài bản Community của Intellij cũng rất xịn rồi :D.</p>\n<h3>Cài đặt Maven</h3>\n<p>Nếu dự án của bạn đã có tồn tại file <strong>pom.xml</strong> do bạn tạo project maven ngay từ đầu thì có thể bỏ qua bước thêm maven framework này.\nCòn nếu dự án đang code không phải là maven project thì bạn sẽ phải convert nó thành maven project trước như hình bên dưới:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 653px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/e7dce/project_tool_window_maven.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Add maven to intellij project\"\n        title=\"Add maven to intellij project\"\n        src=\"/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/e7dce/project_tool_window_maven.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/5a46d/project_tool_window_maven.png 300w,\n/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/0a47e/project_tool_window_maven.png 600w,\n/static/af52c323cff8b85822f4e92227721bae/e7dce/project_tool_window_maven.png 653w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 653px) 100vw, 653px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\nTiếp theo chọn Maven:\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8ed48e8adec3562359baa7270d6f3cd6/12470/add-maven-framework.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Add maven to intellij project\"\n        title=\"Add maven to intellij project\"\n        src=\"/static/8ed48e8adec3562359baa7270d6f3cd6/c1b63/add-maven-framework.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8ed48e8adec3562359baa7270d6f3cd6/5a46d/add-maven-framework.png 300w,\n/static/8ed48e8adec3562359baa7270d6f3cd6/0a47e/add-maven-framework.png 600w,\n/static/8ed48e8adec3562359baa7270d6f3cd6/c1b63/add-maven-framework.png 1200w,\n/static/8ed48e8adec3562359baa7270d6f3cd6/12470/add-maven-framework.png 1311w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Sau đó chúng ta sẽ có file <strong>pom.xml</strong> (Project Object Model) trong project, file này chứa các thông tin cần thiết định nghĩa một dự án như tên dự án, version, nhóm phát triển, các thư viện được sử dụng, các plugins…\nNội dung file sau khi thêm framework:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>project</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>xsi</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xsi:</span>schemaLocation</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>modelVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>4.0.0<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>modelVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>groupId<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>MavenSample<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>1.0-SNAPSHOT<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>maven.compiler.source</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>8<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>maven.compiler.source</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>maven.compiler.target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>8<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>maven.compiler.target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>project</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Chúng ta nên đổi lại thông tin như groupId (id dự án), artifactId (id của app) hay version cho phù hợp. ở đây mình đặt là <strong>com.kiendt</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Thêm thư viện từ Maven vào project.</h3>\n<p>Để thêm thư viện vào maven, chúng ta cần cặp thẻ <em>dependencies</em> để khai báo danh sách thư viện, và cặp thẻ <em>dependency</em> cho từng thư viện cụ thể.</p>\n<p>Cụ thể ở đây chúng ta muốn thêm thư viện <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.microsoft.sqlserver/mssql-jdbc\">Microsoft JDBC Driver For SQL Server</a>, đã nằm sẵn trên trang chủ của maven, việc chúng ta cần làm là lựa chọn version phù hợp với JDK của mình, ở đây mình dùng Java 8 nên mình sẽ dùng phiên bản <a href=\"https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.microsoft.sqlserver/mssql-jdbc/9.2.1.jre8\">9.2.1.jre8</a> như hình:</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/26e3c1d6b4f07493365da53ebe34f09d/d93d9/jdbc-sql-server-maven.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"jdbc sql server maven\"\n        title=\"jdbc sql server maven\"\n        src=\"/static/26e3c1d6b4f07493365da53ebe34f09d/c1b63/jdbc-sql-server-maven.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/26e3c1d6b4f07493365da53ebe34f09d/5a46d/jdbc-sql-server-maven.png 300w,\n/static/26e3c1d6b4f07493365da53ebe34f09d/0a47e/jdbc-sql-server-maven.png 600w,\n/static/26e3c1d6b4f07493365da53ebe34f09d/c1b63/jdbc-sql-server-maven.png 1200w,\n/static/26e3c1d6b4f07493365da53ebe34f09d/d93d9/jdbc-sql-server-maven.png 1243w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Copy đoạn code dành cho Maven và đưa vào file pom.xml, nhớ thêm thẻ <strong>dependencies</strong> wrap lại thẻ dependency.</p>\n<p>Lúc đó file pom.xml sẽ như thế này:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>project</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>xsi</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n         <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xsi:</span>schemaLocation</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/maven-4.0.0.xsd<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>modelVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>4.0.0<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>modelVersion</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>com.kiendt<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>MavenSample<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>1.0-SNAPSHOT<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>maven.compiler.source</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>8<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>maven.compiler.source</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>maven.compiler.target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>8<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>maven.compiler.target</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>properties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dependencies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.microsoft.sqlserver/mssql-jdbc --></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dependency</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>com.microsoft.sqlserver<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>groupId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>mssql-jdbc<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>artifactId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n            <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>9.2.1.jre8<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dependency</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dependencies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>project</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Bước tiếp theo chúng ta cần reload lại project và tải về các thư viện này, mặc định nó sẽ lưu cache lại thư viện lên máy, nên lần tiếp theo nó sẽ lấy trong cache ra mà không download về từ server nếu như trùng version.</p>\n<p>Right click vào <strong>pom.xml</strong> -> Maven -> Reload project.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1200px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bca34e52c166951365d580d92c1383df/d3b46/reload-maven-project.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 64%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"reload maven project\"\n        title=\"reload maven project\"\n        src=\"/static/bca34e52c166951365d580d92c1383df/c1b63/reload-maven-project.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bca34e52c166951365d580d92c1383df/5a46d/reload-maven-project.png 300w,\n/static/bca34e52c166951365d580d92c1383df/0a47e/reload-maven-project.png 600w,\n/static/bca34e52c166951365d580d92c1383df/c1b63/reload-maven-project.png 1200w,\n/static/bca34e52c166951365d580d92c1383df/d3b46/reload-maven-project.png 1690w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Sử dụng driver Microsoft SQL JDBC</h3>\n<p>Xong. Bây giờ việc ta cần làm là dùng JDBC để tương tác với SQL Server.\nTạo 1 class Java tên là <strong>DbContext</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DbContext</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> dbPrefix <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"jdbc:sqlserver://localhost\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> user <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"sa\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> pass <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"123456\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> dbPort <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1433\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> databaseName <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"AccountDB\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Connection</span> <span class=\"token function\">getConnection</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">Connection</span> conn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token class-name\">String</span> dbURL <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> dbPrefix <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\":\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> dbPort <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\";\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"databaseName=\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> databaseName<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token class-name\">DriverManager</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">registerDriver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SQLServerDriver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            conn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">DriverManager</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getConnection</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>dbURL<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> user<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> pass<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">SQLException</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">printStackTrace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> conn<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Tất nhiên sẽ có lỗi khi bạn dán những dòng code phía trên vào, vì bạn chưa import thư viện. Để fix lỗi này, hãy trỏ chuột vào dòng lỗi, nhấn tổ hợp <strong>ALT + Enter</strong>, rồi click import class.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1043px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d164fc10ffc9b6c74c8e259c838287ab/620ae/intellisense-intellij-auto-import.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 71.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"intellij auto import\"\n        title=\"intellij auto import\"\n        src=\"/static/d164fc10ffc9b6c74c8e259c838287ab/620ae/intellisense-intellij-auto-import.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d164fc10ffc9b6c74c8e259c838287ab/5a46d/intellisense-intellij-auto-import.png 300w,\n/static/d164fc10ffc9b6c74c8e259c838287ab/0a47e/intellisense-intellij-auto-import.png 600w,\n/static/d164fc10ffc9b6c74c8e259c838287ab/620ae/intellisense-intellij-auto-import.png 1043w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1043px) 100vw, 1043px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Intellij thần thánh sẽ giúp chúng ta import class từ thư viện JDBC mà không cần phải nhớ tên thư viện để mà dùng Class.forName() củ chuối nữa.\nVà đây là kết quả cuối cùng, các bạn có thể dùng phương thức getConnection() để sử dụng ở bất kì đâu.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1032px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a4dafcdc0af071023919b550c0d6fda6/12bff/final-code-result.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.00000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Code after importing sql server driver\"\n        title=\"Code after importing sql server driver\"\n        src=\"/static/a4dafcdc0af071023919b550c0d6fda6/12bff/final-code-result.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a4dafcdc0af071023919b550c0d6fda6/5a46d/final-code-result.png 300w,\n/static/a4dafcdc0af071023919b550c0d6fda6/0a47e/final-code-result.png 600w,\n/static/a4dafcdc0af071023919b550c0d6fda6/12bff/final-code-result.png 1032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1032px) 100vw, 1032px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Kết</h2>\n<p>Hi vọng sau bài viết này bạn sẽ có khả năng sử dụng maven để hoàn thành các bài tập và từ bỏ Eclipse sida để quay về với Intellij - con đường chánh đạo. Happy coding !</p>"},"primaryTag":{"name":"Java","color":"#007acc"}},"pageContext":{"postId":"7424cdf0-c7a0-5576-a5ad-5e0f9820ff12","primaryTag":"Java"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1116962356","1994268275","2206391224","2275848304","545095672"]}